{"type":"article","id":1400,"title":"南京市人社局关于南京应用技术学校情况的通报","uid":1,"topics":[1873,274,1890],"contents":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb1f6UcAA2MEE?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb1f6UcAA2MEE?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb1f6UcAA2MEE?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb3MZUEAA3qZC?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb3MZUEAA3qZC?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb3MZUEAA3qZC?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n4月29日，南京市人社局发布通报称，南京应用技术学校私自与他校合作办学，以本校名义虚假招生，承诺护理专业大专文凭、护士资格证等，因无法兑现而导致学生不满。此外，社会闲散人员借机穿着特勤制服殴打学生与家长，与本事件无关，当地公安已采取果断措施控制了学生与家长，学生、家长表示情绪稳定。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb3T8UUAAn5cT?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb3T8UUAAn5cT?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5Sb3T8UUAAn5cT?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-04-29","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}